# Tailwind CSS

Use Tailwind utilities.

Avoid inline styles.

Avoid custom CSS unless necessary.

Prefer utility classes.

## Layout

Use:

max-w-7xl

mx-auto

px-6

md:px-10

lg:px-16

## Spacing

Prefer:

gap

flex

grid

instead of margins.

## Responsive

Always build mobile first.

Then:

md

lg

xl

## Colors

Use Tailwind theme variables.

Avoid hardcoded colors unless part of the design system.